{"tid":1454574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[十八區文宣日播夜播]黑警濫暴私刑合集","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T08:32:42.000Z","uid":293635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d574e82027f8be8146262cbb54fabcdba43a0c9a","tid":1454574,"uid":293635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:49:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/T5hv4mfo4g8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FT5hv4mfo4g8&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=d113173a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/T5hv4mfo4g8</a><br />\n<br />\n(代post)我朋友眼見狗隻暴行罄竹難書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個個星期都有新野，為免大家唔記得狗隻做過咩，佢地幫大家砌左條610-811期間部分警暴合集<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位拎部projector落各區連儂牆、港鐵站、樓下屋苑配合文宣日播夜播，提醒全香港人黑警兩個幾月黎點樣殘害香港人，大巴大巴車落講大話聲稱警察克制用武恰當的垃圾高官同垃圾藍絲，話佢地知香港警察點樣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">知法犯法<br />\n不斷謀殺<br />\n全部垃圾</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n片段擷自各媒體，恕不逐一說明出處，本影片亦只選取部分事件，如有不足，敬請見諒！！！歡迎使用，日播夜播！！！！<br />\n<br />\n呢到只係針對黑警暴行，但重點依然係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">五大訴求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好放過個政府，所有人要繼續出黎繼續抗爭！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"766fa9f20d9e92de0f1c232d3d9ca6dc147479e7","tid":1454574,"uid":35633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T07:25:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fe0948c254776b4d931381e157cdcfad0bea199","tid":1454574,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}